        "content": "<p>My brief glance gives me the impression that this is based on symbolic ai. I wonder is there a linguistic component in the project? I personally am interested in bringing back the value of symbolic ai and linguistics in the context of llms. This seems a promising direction. Is there any timeline on published work or info?</p>",
