        "sender_full_name": "Xiyu Zhai",
        "timestamp": 1722998562
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes, the tool which does this informalization is not public, which is quite frustrating to me (as I have already expressed to <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110031\">@Patrick Massot</span> ) because I have projects that would like to build upon this tool and are currently in a holding pattern until it is released</p>",
        "id": 457217658,
        "sender_full_name": "Mario Carneiro",
        "timestamp": 1723070977
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Personally I believe informalization is a direction where many research could be conducted to find the best way to do things. And I believe we should make things as open as possible. A closed source translation loses much of the trust we could have on a symbolic system.</p>",
        "id": 457227942,
